 800 REM === Wire cut ===
 810 IF k$=w$ THEN GO TO 1000
 900 REM === EXPLOSION ===
 910 FOR i=1 TO 25
 920 BORDER INT (RND*8)
 930 BEEP 0.02,INT (RND*40)
 940 NEXT i
 950 BORDER 2
 960 INK 2: LET g=0: GO SUB 2400
 970 LET r=15: LET t$="BOOM!": INK 2: BRIGHT 1: FLASH 1: GO SUB 3000: FLASH 0: BRIGHT 0
 980 LET r=21: GO SUB 3100: LET t$="Correct wire was "+w$: INK 5: GO SUB 3000
 990 STOP
1000 REM === DEFUSED! ===
1010 FOR i=1 TO 15
1020 BORDER 4: BEEP 0.02,25+i*2
1030 BORDER 0: BEEP 0.02,25+i*2
1040 NEXT i
1050 BORDER 4
1060 INK 4: LET g=t: GO SUB 2400
1070 REM === Turn LEDs green ===
1080 INK 4: CIRCLE 80,160,2: CIRCLE 88,160,2: CIRCLE 96,160,2
1090 CIRCLE 160,160,2: CIRCLE 168,160,2: CIRCLE 176,160,2
1100 LET r=15: LET t$="DEFUSED!": INK 4: BRIGHT 1: FLASH 1: GO SUB 3000: FLASH 0: BRIGHT 0
1110 LET r=21: GO SUB 3100: LET t$="Time left: "+STR$ t+" seconds": INK 5: GO SUB 3000
1120 BEEP 0.5,30
1130 STOP
